title: 이달의소녀탐구 #128 (LOONA TV #128)
summary:
0:02 -- Kim Lip is informed that her stage name has changed to Kim Lip and she gets
shocked. At the same time, we hear something falling in the background
0:10 -- She is asked about how she feels about her new name. “Are you serious?” and
hesitatingly, “I need to put myself together…”
